  "title": "INDUSTRIAL ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for someone who is innovative, resourceful and proactive with a passion for engineering. <br /><br /><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Review production schedules, processes, specifications, and related information</li><li>Design production processes that maximize efficiency and reduce waste</li><li>Develop and implement process improvements and technological upgrades</li><li>Design control systems to minimize costs and production issues</li><li>Develop design and production standards in cooperation with management and user personnel</li><li>Prepare material and equipment lists, purchase orders, cost analyses, and estimated production costs</li><li>Design the layout of facilities and determine personnel requirements</li><li>Train staff for new processes and provide instructions and manuals</li><li>Manage process documentation and prepare production reports</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Specification</strong></u></p><ul><li>Knowledge of precision machining, production scheduling and production management</li><li>Knowledge of production scheduling and production control</li><li>Knowledge of engineering drawing interpretation</li><li>Knowledge of part manufacturability</li><li>Knowledge of Environment, Health & Safety</li><li>Knowledge of Fire Safety of factory & office premises</li><li>Preferably with 3 years of relevant working experience in precision machining industry</li><li>Diploma or higher qualification in Industrial Engineering, Precision Engineering or Manufacturing</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
